<p>in thorough agreement with her &amp; that is the absolute uncertainty of life today<br/>None of us is secure for five minutes together.<br/>It is hard for a man to follow out his ideals honestly under these circumstances, for every hour is a tremendous struggle.  But if he gives in &amp; flows with the tide he is only choosing the shadow &amp; sooner or later he will return to search for the substance<br/>No letters from Rita again this mail.<br/>I do so want to have a nice long letter from the dear little girl to encourage me</p>
